{"heading":"Rejoice in the Lord—Sing unto Him a new song—He loves righteousness and judgment—Blessed is the nation whose God is the Lord.","number":33,"verseCount":22,"verses":[[1,["Rejoice in the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", O ye righteous: ",["for",["clarity-word"]]," ",["praise",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 147:1","ot/ps/147.1"],"; ",["Alma 26:8","bofm/alma/26.8"],"; ",["D&C 136:28 (28–29)","dc-testament/dc/136.28"],"."]]]," is comely for the upright."]],[2,["Praise the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," with harp: sing unto him with the psaltery ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," an instrument of ten strings."]],[3,["Sing unto him a ",["new song",["study-note-ref","a",["IE raise also fresh, new praises and thanks to God for His ever-new blessings. ",["Ps. 40:3","ot/ps/40.3"],"; ",["D&C 25:12","dc-testament/dc/25.12"],"."]]],"; play skilfully with a loud noise."]],[4,["For the ",["word",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 84:45","dc-testament/dc/84.45"],"."]]]," of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," right; and all his works ",["are done",["clarity-word"]]," in truth."]],[5,["He loveth ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]]," and ",["judgment",["study-note-ref","b",["HEB justice."]]],": the earth is ",["full",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ps. 119:64","ot/ps/119.64"],"."]]]," of the goodness of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"."]],[6,["By the ",["word",["study-note-ref","a",["See ",["JST John 1:1–16 (Appendix)","jst/jst-john/1.1-16"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Creator","tg/jesus-christ-creator"],"."]]]," of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," were the ",["heavens",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Heaven","tg/heaven"],"."]]]," made; and all the host of them by the breath of his mouth."]],[7,["He gathereth the waters of the sea together as an heap: he layeth up the depth in storehouses."]],[8,["Let all the earth fear the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]]